title: How Do: Garen

embed.description: 3 points and 2 comments so far on reddit

body:
A month of gathering clips, and frustrating 3rd party replay tools ( riot pls ) and 10 HOURS of editing. It's done. My first ever OverEdit project, with more to come.

Reddit upvotes are appreciated, but only if you think it's worthy.

Also, feel free to leave comments and such here. If you wanna contact me personally, I never leave twitter :3

Cheers guys.

~J
